---
// Speaks to the engineer who ships the agent — the buyer-influencer who
// changed the prompt/model/tools and needs a trustworthy verdict without
// building a review pipeline. Distinct from the engineer-as-reviewer persona
// in Audience.astro: this is the person who shipped and needs the loop closed.
// Intentionally no CTAs — CtaFooter is the single closing conversion band.
---

<section class="py-14 lg:py-20">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="reveal">
      <p
        class="font-mono text-[11px] tracking-[0.18em] text-muted-foreground uppercase"
      >
        For the engineer who ships
      </p>
      <h2
        class="mt-3 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-foreground sm:text-3xl"
      >
        You changed the agent. Get a verdict you can trust.
      </h2>
      <p
        class="mt-4 max-w-2xl text-base leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground sm:text-lg"
      >
        You shipped a change &mdash; new prompt, model, or tool &mdash; and need
        to know it got better. Send one link instead of building a review
        pipeline. Judgment comes back structured, tied to the exact version and
        trace, ready for a regression set or your next revision.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div
      class="reveal reveal-delay-1 mt-8 rounded-xl border border-border/60 bg-card p-5 sm:mt-10 sm:p-6"
    >
      <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-3">
        <span
          class="font-mono text-[10px] tracking-[0.18em] text-primary uppercase"
        >
          Verdict
        </span>
        <span
          class="font-mono text-[10px] tracking-[0.14em] text-muted-foreground uppercase"
        >
          Blind review closed
        </span>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm font-semibold text-foreground">
        Candidate preferred &middot; 7 of 9 reviewers
      </p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground italic">
        &ldquo;Tighter recovery when the tool call failed &mdash; it retried
        instead of guessing.&rdquo;
      </p>
      <div
        class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-x-2 gap-y-1 border-t border-border/60 pt-3 font-mono text-[11px] text-muted-foreground"
      >
        <span>v14</span>
        <span aria-hidden="true">&middot;</span>
        <span>trace #&hellip;482</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
